<img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1370568" title="macitynet.it" src="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/powerbank-apple-watch.jpg" alt="macitynet.it" width="1200" height="826" srcset="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/powerbank-apple-watch.jpg 1200w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/powerbank-apple-watch-480x330.jpg 480w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/powerbank-apple-watch-50x34.jpg 50w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/powerbank-apple-watch-75x52.jpg 75w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/powerbank-apple-watch-100x70.jpg 100w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/powerbank-apple-watch-200x138.jpg 200w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/powerbank-apple-watch-500x344.jpg 500w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/powerbank-apple-watch-610x420.jpg 610w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/powerbank-apple-watch-218x150.jpg 218w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/powerbank-apple-watch-696x479.jpg 696w,   https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/powerbank-apple-watch-1068x735.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" />
 
Se una batteria come quella di Satechi vi pare ingombrante o se non avete da ricaricare niente altro che il vostro Apple Watch, questa powerbank è perfetta. Si tratta di un piccolo accumulatore da 5000 mAh, sufficienti per ricaricare almeno quattro volte Apple Watch. La forma a portachiavi è compatta e pratica, rendendo la batteria facile da trasportare. Un LED mostra la capacità residua.
